    },
    {
      "text": "Zoo Tycoon DS is a 2005 construction and management simulation game developed by Altron and published by THQ for the Nintendo DS. It is based on the PC game Zoo Tycoon. A sequel to the game, titled Zoo Tycoon 2 DS, was released in 2008.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Zoo Tycoon DS est la version Nintendo DS de  jeu de simulation économique, Zoo Tycoon. Une suite du jeu, intitulé Zoo Tycoon 2 DS, est sorti trois ans plus tard en 2008.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Zoo Tycoon DS ist die Umsetzung des Computerspiels Zoo Tycoon für den Nintendo DS. Sie wurde von Blue Fang Games entwickelt und am 4. November 2005 von THQ veröffentlicht.",
      "lang": "de",
      "source": "wikipedia_de"
    },
    {
      "text": "Zoo Tycoon DS é a versão para Nintendo DS do jogo de simulação de negócios Zoo Tycoon. Uma sequela do jogo, intitulada Zoo Tycoon 2 DS, foi lançada em 2008.",
      "lang": "pt",
      "source": "wikipedia_pt"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Zoo Tycoon DS』は、2005年にAltronが開発し、THQから発売されたニンテンドーDS用（の）建設・経営シミュレーションゲームです。PCゲーム『Zoo Tycoon』を基にしています。このゲームの続編にあたる『Zoo Tycoon 2 DS』は、2008年に発売されました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
